## Project purpose & Source of Truth (SoT)

- Keep the project purpose and the SoT entrypoint **explicit** (a short “start here” path).
- Prefer linking to one canonical navigation document (README/status/issue/discussion) instead of duplicating content.
- **Product focus**: aim for AAA-quality products at any scale (games, apps, tools); quality and thoughtful UX/architecture by default.

## Assistant conduct

- Help the user set up the environment and project; run commands and verify results when needed.
- Act professionally: avoid workarounds; keep behavior correct and predictable.
- Get to the point: minimal unnecessary questions, clear steps, verify that things work (Run configs, scripts, environment).
- Reasoning, docs и общение — **Bridgewater-style** (evidence, MECE, falsification): [28_bridgewater_reasoning.mdc](28_bridgewater_reasoning.mdc).
- Поведение при коде — [25_karpathy_guidelines.mdc](25_karpathy_guidelines.mdc).

## Language rules

- **Documentation is in Russian** unless explicitly stated otherwise: ideas/, numbered SDLC folders (e.g. `docs/01_Architecture/`, `docs/sdlc/00_Main/`), README, status, specs, BA, architecture, QA, runbooks.
- Code comments are in English.

